Class MajorPane

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.MajorPane

  • public class MajorPane
extends java.lang.Object
    Major Pane class will build A Pane using JavaFx that allows the user to create a major. The user will enter a major name and then press enter where a second screen will pop up. In that screen the user will be ale to chose which course he would like to make up that major. User then closes the stage and the major is created.
    Author:
    Caio Eugenio
